=====================
/makercore

Python module that uses OCE internally to provide

Geometry:
	Body
	(Surface)
	Curve3d
	Shape2d
	(Curve2d)


TriangleMesh

Classes are wrapped with Boost.Python into module "_makercore", then extended (not inherited) in the python module called makercore.

Dependencies:
	OCE
	Boost.Python


======================
/makercad

Python application

Dependencies
	Qt4
	PySide
	PyOpenGL
	makercore

